{"tid":2335073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳門宣布香港及英國等地入境後須集中隔離21日","createTime":"2020-12-21T14:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T14:35:08.000Z","uid":278587,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"144bcd01d6a78ab6e45c21c8e90f45ceabd6b3d2","tid":2335073,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:31:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=417470\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417470&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=a4ff324c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417470&h=bf5c9b94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=417470</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】澳門宣布收緊防疫措施，由香港及英國等地入境須集中隔離21日。<br />\n<br />\n新措施晚上十時起生效，過去14日到過內地及台灣以外地方的所有入境人士，包括香港及英國，入境後須於指定酒店隔離21日，較原本檢疫期延長7日，至於正在隔離的人，檢疫期亦會延長至21日，並須在隔離第20日再接受核酸病毒檢測。<br />\n<br />\n澳門政府指，英國病毒變種，加上不同地方都曾出現十四天隔離後的社區確診個案，有必要加強措施。"},{"pid":"bf0795e818a1c9253081b0d3d64a2ba72bac7cab","tid":2335073,"uid":220833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"賀一城ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56eb9a9831d5d9d3a11c9889a6f60f3929192c5e","tid":2335073,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:35:08.000Z","msg":"教撚埋柒婆點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}